rows.label: qst700104_msg0101
rows.name:
There's no need to be
afraid. Come with us.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0201
rows.name: Yonma-san, we've been looking for you.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0202
rows.name: Come now, let's go home together.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0301
rows.name: Good, you seem to be unharmed.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0302
rows.name: Let's see... Ajijii? Yonma? Time to go.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0401
rows.name: Found you... You're coming with me.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0402
rows.name: And I won't take no for an answer.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0601
rows.name: You are Yonma... is that correct?

rows.label: qst700104_msg0602
rows.name: Don't be scared. Come on over.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0701
rows.name: Did you enjoy the fresh air?

rows.label: qst700104_msg0702
rows.name: Come on, let's go home... Good girl.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0801
rows.name:
Greetings. We have been
searching for you.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0802
rows.name:
I am Wadatsumi. I will take
responsibility and see you
returned to your master.
